# mirdan Debug Mode — DEPRECATED

**DEPRECATED: mirdan-debug is retired in 2.1.0.**

Debug inline using Cursor's main chat. If the fix touches a file tracked in
a three-layer plan under `docs/plans/`, call
`mcp__mirdan__validate_code_quality` after the fix and, if plan coverage
matters, `mcp__mirdan__verify_plan_against_brief` on the plan.

This rule will be removed in 2.2.0.
